name: 1983 Highlight Sade Baderinwa - thr33smas Insert - #3MAS10
description:
The Tenth Day of thr33smas

Tenth card in a series of 12 cards looking back at the highlights of the first 7 months of thr33som3s mints.

Throughout October, The Grotto rallied its support around thr33som3s nomination for the first ever NFT Award as Best Non-Digital Artist at NFT.NYC.

With the win secured, thr33som3s made his first public appearance November 2nd at the awards ceremony.   Presenting the award was Action Team 7 anchor, Sade Barderinwa.  Little did she know, her life would never be quite the same.

This card commemorates the moment Sade Baderinwa fell forever in love with thr33som3s. As thr33som3s said, "they always come around."

The 12 Days of thr33smas is a chase 3v3nt. Collect all 12, #3MAS1 through #3MAS12, in the announced timeframe to receive #3MAS13 via airdrop.

This card is an INSERT. It has all established Standard Insert Utility and may compound additional Utilities over time. It is a Painting Insert, a thr33smas Insert and a Holiday Insert. ***** digital capture of original painting, gouache on vintage baseball card, 2021. ************ NFT image is for personal use, no commercial rights are granted. Twitter @thr33som3s and IG @thr33somes to see upcoming cards and new series. ************ ALL thr33som3s have FUTURE UTILITY.
